            <div id="iixs5y" class="col in2une_global faq">
                <div id="iq6i37">
                    <div id="ivrxys" class="faq">
                        <div id="i9nyzf">
                            <p id="iw6u0k" title="faq">Have a Question? <span draggable="true" data-highlightable="1" target="#ctrwow-accordion" hide-target-on-init="" id="iefp89" class="js-toggle-trigger"><span draggable="true" data-highlightable="1" id="igfx1d">See Our FAQs</span></span>
                        </div>
                        <div id="ctrwow-accordion" class="ctrwow-accordion_global">
                            <ul id="i4ryuz" class="accordion js-accordion">
                                <li id="ipx5gk" class="accordion__item js-accordion__item">
                                    <button type="button" id="ifkls7" class="accordion__header js-tab-focus"><span id="i4vnzu" class="text-md"><span id="i3z4dkr" draggable="true">Question:</span><span id="icbael9">Is ULTRARADIANCE safe to use?</span></span><em aria-hidden="true" id="idj8r35" class="accordion__icon-wrapper"><img data-lazy-srcsets="&lt;767:,&lt;1023:,>1023:https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png" id="ixi92vf"  src="https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png"  class="ctr-lazy-image" width="1" height="1"></em></button>
                                    <div id="izw3p7c" class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel">
                                        <div id="ig6kti1" class="text-component">
                                            <div id="ia7hdj">Yes. Light therapy is delivered in a safe method that allows you to use the device at home. ULTRARADIANCE also has a safety feature that will shut off after 10 minutes to ensure you do not exceed the suggested time per session.</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                <li id="if5oyqr" class="accordion__item js-accordion__item">
                                    <button type="button" id="ix6vhan" class="accordion__header js-tab-focus"><span id="is5e68n" class="text-md"><span draggable="true" id="ivlzwbh">Question:</span><span id="imdztm4">How long until I see results?</span></span><em aria-hidden="true" id="i9lxwat" class="accordion__icon-wrapper"><img data-lazy-srcsets="&lt;767:,&lt;1023:,>1023:https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png" id="ixyzwjs"  src="https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png"  class="ctr-lazy-image" width="1" height="1"></em></button>
                                    <div id="iqvzm0l" class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel">
                                        <div id="ibhm8bh" class="text-component">
                                            <div id="iz7d5xk">Results vary depending on several factors such as skin type, skin conditions, intensity of light, frequency of sessions, and your personal skin goals. ULTRARADIANCE suggests 3-5 sessions per week.</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                <li id="iiufhre" class="accordion__item js-accordion__item">
                                    <button type="button" id="ijofub5" class="accordion__header js-tab-focus"><span id="icf0h1o" class="text-md"><span draggable="true" id="i5lwabh">Question:</span><span id="ib3gelz">How do I know which light to use?</span></span><em aria-hidden="true" id="ie55ada" class="accordion__icon-wrapper"><img data-lazy-srcsets="&lt;767:,&lt;1023:,>1023:https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png" id="i07ty7j"  src="https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png"  class="ctr-lazy-image" width="1" height="1"></em></button>
                                    <div id="ij5c2zk" class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel">
                                        <div id="igkhl8z" class="text-component">
                                            <div id="i40d3b9">
                                                You can determine which light will give you the best results depending on your skin goals. Each light serves a different purpose:
                                                <div id="i1p96ey">RED – Supports skin elasticity</div>
                                                <div id="i6k86za">GREEN – Smooths out dark spots and evens skin tone</div>
                                                <div id="id4h2ig">YELLOW – Improves blood flow, brightens complexion</div>
                                                <div id="idev9z1">PINK – Whitens skin and gives your skin a natural glow</div>
                                                <div id="ih6w8cw">FLASH – Boosts results of skin products by permeating the products into your skin</div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                <li id="iaax7hr" class="accordion__item js-accordion__item">
                                    <button type="button" id="i7e71uv" class="accordion__header js-tab-focus"><span id="ibla0si" class="text-md"><span draggable="true" id="i342zfh">Question:</span><span id="ixwlzq2">How long should I use ULTRARADIANCE for?</span></span><em aria-hidden="true" id="i6bi6il" class="accordion__icon-wrapper"><img data-lazy-srcsets="&lt;767:,&lt;1023:,>1023:https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png" id="igqjzgd"  src="https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png"  class="ctr-lazy-image" width="1" height="1"></em></button>
                                    <div id="iuwbj54" class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel">
                                        <div id="i9magvj" class="text-component">
                                            <div id="intth0i">You can use ULTRARADIANCE for as long as you need to. Even if you reach your skin goals, you can continue to use the device for maintenance and touchups.</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                <li id="i7k3sht" class="accordion__item js-accordion__item">
                                    <button type="button" id="i1cwoke" class="accordion__header js-tab-focus"><span id="i947ejo" class="text-md"><span draggable="true" id="i0gtl9h">Question:</span><span id="i9tqad6">Does ULTRARADIANCE light therapy hurt?</span></span><em aria-hidden="true" id="i980s3i" class="accordion__icon-wrapper"><img data-lazy-srcsets="&lt;767:,&lt;1023:,>1023:https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png" id="ic8lbly"  src="https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png"  class="ctr-lazy-image" width="1" height="1"></em></button>
                                    <div id="i2m17hi" class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel">
                                        <div id="irogppe" class="text-component">
                                            <div id="ijc54xb">ULTRARADIANCE can feel warm or tingly. Everyone’s skin is different, so others may be more sensitive to the laser therapy.</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                <li id="ix0y2l9" class="accordion__item js-accordion__item">
                                    <button type="button" id="izi4mxw" class="accordion__header js-tab-focus"><span id="iy1kbfh" class="text-md"><span draggable="true" id="iiy3mzz">Question:</span><span id="ij3ft7g">Do I have to use a serum with ULTRARADIANCE?</span></span><em aria-hidden="true" id="i35cxla" class="accordion__icon-wrapper"><img data-lazy-srcsets="&lt;767:,&lt;1023:,>1023:https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png" id="ih6cu0k"  src="https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png"  class="ctr-lazy-image" width="1" height="1"></em></button>
                                    <div id="iohx7cv" class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel">
                                        <div id="imnrzok" class="text-component">
                                            <div id="inrop3r">ULTRARADIANCE can be used alone or with a serum to compliment your skin treatment.</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                <li id="ip1e8lf" class="accordion__item js-accordion__item">
                                    <button type="button" id="ilduaj6" class="accordion__header js-tab-focus"><span id="izehciy" class="text-md"><span draggable="true" id="i7b5zat">Question:</span><span id="inmnwwb">Is there any downtime after a session?</span></span><em aria-hidden="true" id="ikbwccf" class="accordion__icon-wrapper"><img data-lazy-srcsets="&lt;767:,&lt;1023:,>1023:https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png" id="i0wlfcl"  src="https://ctrwow-commonstorage.azureedge.net/public-assets/back.png"  class="ctr-lazy-image" width="1" height="1"></em></button>
                                    <div id="if1buwi" class="accordion__panel js-accordion__panel">
                                        <div id="ihpjyc3" class="text-component">
                                            <div id="io8rcr3">Everyone’s skin is different and may react differently after each session.</div>
                                        </div>
